    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "### 1. 제로-설정 액세스 (기본값)"
  },
  {
    "row": 52,
    "rowsha": "POBqVx4Pc+lbLEvuzhyI9RxAn3sJqsqXHsp0Posm/1k=",
    "originContent": "### 1. Zero-Config Access (Default)",
    "translatedContent": "간단히 사용해보고 싶다면, 설치 프로그램이 **퀵 터널** URL을 제공합니다:"
  },
  {
    "row": 53,
    "rowsha": "ZmYbwovB9L6Ez01L7a6vdSGNOXQSe3ylmLed8CS/JPI=",
    "originContent": "If you just want to try it out, the installer provides a **Quick Tunnel** URL:",
    "translatedContent": "`https://<random-name>.trycloudflare.com/?key=<YOUR_KEY>`"
  },
  {
    "row": 54,
    "rowsha": "OHOEGk4b40SjNX4otgv1M58evVg6/NIG+jg9CWE0Gvc=",
    "originContent": "`https://<random-name>.trycloudflare.com/?key=<YOUR_KEY>`",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 55,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "*   **장점**: 어디서나 즉시 접속 가능."
  },
  {
    "row": 56,
    "rowsha": "7WLKIooynKh7vDWG+Gnx2ktUAkRm/HNTe+GULjr0UXs=",
    "originContent": "*   **Pros**: Instant access from anywhere.",
    "translatedContent": "*   **단점**: 서비스를 재시작하면 URL이 변경됩니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 57,
    "rowsha": "EJlaAu5CJCziBUtwRwSINiOW/dEoWyVt7LPFH/AxWxM=",
    "originContent": "*   **Cons**: URL changes if you restart the service.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 58,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "### 2. VPN 직접 액세스 (개인정보 우선)"
  },
  {
    "row": 59,
    "rowsha": "mKLcEZmFgLQt/mco8YIVkBUFNLQot2+x9rwDe1NUcNU=",
    "originContent": "### 2. VPN Direct Access (Privacy First)",
    "translatedContent": "**Tailscale** 또는 **WireGuard**가 감지되면, 설치 프로그램은 공개 터널을 건너뛰고 개인 링크를 제공합니다:"
  },
  {
    "row": 60,
    "rowsha": "N+ZS4ohoK+8MlAn5VOvw6YIvkS3F0V31BXXhyAGeaEE=",
    "originContent": "If **Tailscale** or **WireGuard** is detected, the installer skips the public tunnel and gives you a private link:",
    "translatedContent": "`http://<VPN_IP>:3000/?key=<YOUR_KEY>`"
  },
  {
    "row": 61,
    "rowsha": "HKk+N3HqmJWoabnUVrZNVKNwV9G2rrZzK3z5+L0zy7I=",
    "originContent": "`http://<VPN_IP>:3000/?key=<YOUR_KEY>`",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 62,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "*   **장점**: 가장 빠른 속도, 최대 개인정보 보호."
  },
  {
    "row": 63,
    "rowsha": "ptZmHP3lwLKYUnlRCnkrJAAcuB9woAj7SEX5flDpBEg=",
    "originContent": "*   **Pros**: Fastest speed, maximum privacy.",
    "translatedContent": "*   **단점**: 휴대폰이 VPN에 연결되어 있어야 합니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 64,
    "rowsha": "ZCGnKzxeAqtr8w8VeivpN4itz60+F5dq5de7RvRxkhc=",
    "originContent": "*   **Cons**: Your phone must be connected to the VPN.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 65,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "### 3. 영구 공개 도메인 (고급)"
  },
  {
    "row": 66,
    "rowsha": "0CFetpxl2KSfNG4Vc+PesjuFzL0NaXWeaAERFe6OrT0=",
    "originContent": "### 3. Permanent Public Domain (Advanced)",
    "translatedContent": "`dash.yoursite.com` 같은 고정 URL을 원하십니까?"
  },
  {
    "row": 67,
    "rowsha": "ykILoXjKTIr+nB9xHyshLkeaR4DnEpZqkd8eBJWv7HY=",
    "originContent": "Want a fixed URL like `dash.yoursite.com`?",
    "translatedContent": "1.  [Cloudflare 대시보드 \\> 네트워킹 \\> 터널](https://dash.cloudflare.com/?to=/:account/tunnels)에서 **Cloudflare 터널 토큰**을 받으세요."
  },
  {
